name: Mupix9
author: Mupix
description:
Mupix9
 is a simple and compact master palette for multi-purpose usage. The 
intention behind this palette is to show how versatile some shades can 
be. The teal shades can be used for water, sky, and even foliage, while 
the browns and yellows can be used for dirt, tree trunks, and skin 
tones.
